OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779894668
OL,3,CWoman pleads guilty after teenage
OL,4,Ccousin dies in XL bully attack
OL,6,FA woman from Bristol has admitted to
OL,7,Fbeing in charge of a dog dangerously
OL,8,Fout of control after her teenage
OL,9,Fcousin died in an XL bully attack.
OL,11,F24-year-old Kelsie Reed, of Lawrence
OL,12,FWeston, has pleaded guilty to being in
OL,13,Fcharge of a dog dangerously out of
OL,14,Fcontrol in Bristol Crown Court on
OL,15,FWednesday 27 May.
OL,17,FMorgan Dorsett, from Shropshire, was
OL,18,Fattacked by the dog, named Prince, in
OL,19,Fa flat in Withywood in February last
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
