PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779894668
OL,3,CWoman pleads guilty after teenage
OL,4,Ccousin dies in XL bully attack
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,7,Fproperty in Cobhorn Drive at 7.19pm
OL,8,Fbut despite their efforts, Ms Dorsett
OL,9,Fdied.
OL,11,FThe 19-year-old had suffered fatal
OL,12,Fbites to her neck during the incident.
OL,14,FThe dog was put down afterwards.
OL,16,FKelsie Reed wept in court as she read
OL,17,Fout her guilty plea and was comforted
OL,18,Fby a family member.
OL,20,FSentencing will take place on 9 July.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
